Piccup -- a simple image viewer/uploader/downloader.

Features :
    - minimal configuration
    - lazy creation of thumbnails
    - easy username/password setup
    - per-user directories
    - REST interface

Installation :

Piccup daemon

Sample configuration file :

{
    "thumb_dir" : "/var/thumbs",
    "upload_base" : "/var/piccup",
    "sam" : {
        "pw" : "foo",
        "dirs" : [ "/some/dir/someplace" ]
     },
    "pippin" : {
        "pw" : "bar",
        "dirs" : [ "/var/piccup/*" ]
}



